            <title>麻雀直播玩家留言太暴力   ABEMA 用 AI 監察評論並自動封鎖觀眾</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/13/abema-mahjong-use-ai-detect-comment/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=abema-mahjong-use-ai-detect-comment</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/13/abema-mahjong-use-ai-detect-comment/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 10:56:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ABEMA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1204293</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本網絡電視台 ABEMA 的 CyberAgent 上週五（11 月 10 日）宣佈將會利用 AI 功能監控「麻雀頻道」上出現的誹謗和騷擾言論，以遏制用户騷擾玩家的歪風。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1204379" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5719.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5720.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1204376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5720-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5720-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5720-415x900.png 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5720.png 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_5720-709x1536.png 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲麻雀直播節目的留言區出現大量「專家」有些留言甚至有攻擊性</p><p>ABMEA 會利用 AI 監控評論功能及其他使用者舉報來判斷發言是否有誹謗性質。如判定該評論有誹謗性質的話，會在一段時間內暫停用户發表評論。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1204310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/l_ts0153_abema02-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/l_ts0153_abema02-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/l_ts0153_abema02.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲被停用評論後的畫面，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2311/10/news176.html">ITMedia.co.jp</a></p><p>ABEMA 表示會重複確認觀眾的評論是否有惡意，如果確認有惡意後，ABEMA 會與律師事務所合作，按照提供者責任限制法披露發佈惡意言論用户的個人訊息，並向警方提供損害報告及提出訴訟，「營造玩家能夠安心打牌的環境」。ABEMA 麻將頻道會播放許多專業麻將節目，包括轉播日本首個跨組織的職業隊制競技麻將聯盟「M 聯盟」的比賽。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2311/10/news176.html">ITmedia.co.jp</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>====</p><h2>unwire learn 推出:</h2><p><strong>獨門 AI 用法助你工作及創業課程</strong><br />
